  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety With Albumin-bound Paclitaxel (Abraxane) in the TAC as Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy in Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study to Assess the Efficacy and Safety With Albumin-bound Paclitaxel (Abraxane) in the TAC as Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy in the Treatment of Operable Breast Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
