  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Select 60 cases of women with breast cancer at clinical stage of T1-4N0-2M0. Then treat them
      with 4 cycles of TAC (Abraxane 260mg/m2,EPI 60 mg/m2 ,CTX 500 mg/m2, 21day/cycle) as
      neoadjuvant chemotherapy. Finally the investigators assess the efficacy and safety of
      Albumin-bound Paclitaxel.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators select 60 cases of women with breast cancer at clinical stage of
      T1-4N0-2M0. Then treat them with 4 cycles of TAC (Abraxane 260mg/m2,EPI 60 mg/m2 ,CTX 500
      mg/m2, 21day/cycle) as neoadjuvant chemotherapy. Finally the investigators assess the
      efficacy and safety of Albumin-bound Paclitaxel.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
